Package edu.ncsu.csc216.issue_manager.model.manager

Class IssueManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.issue_manager.model.manager.IssueManager
  • public class IssueManager
extends java.lang.Object
    IssueManager is responsible for the entire life cycle of issueList. IssueManager can keep track of issues, getIssuesByType, displayIssuesAsAnArray, saveIssuesToFile, loadIssuesFromFile, create a new issue list, getIssueById, execute commands on issues, deleting issues, and adding issues to the issue list. IssueManager follows a singelton pattern so only one instance of IssueManager will ever be created.
    Author:
    michaelabrams
